gitCommit.subject: Enhance E2E tests and rate limiting configuration
gitCommit.body:
Enhance E2E tests and rate limiting configuration

- Added debug logging for rate limiting environment variables.
- Updated rate limiting middleware to apply before route registration.
- Modified E2E tests to use valid email addresses for login.
- Implemented API token retrieval in E2E tests for authentication.
- Improved error handling for API responses in tests.
- Ensured localStorage is set with access tokens before page reloads in tests.
